title: Wine 9.0 Released with Experimental Wayland Graphics Driver
description:
Wine 9.0 free and open-source compatibility layer for running Windows games and apps on Unix-like operating systems is now available. Here's what's new!

title: VirtualBox 7.0.14 Lets You Import and Export VMs with NVMe Storage Controllers
description:
VirtualBox 7.0.14 open-source virtualization software is now available for download with support for importing and exporting VMs containing NVMe storage controllers and initial support for RHEL 9.4's kernel.

title: XOrg Server and Xwayland Patched Against Multiple Security Vulnerabilities
description:
XOrg Server 21.1.11 and Xwayland 23.2.4 have been released today to address a total of six security vulnerabilities. Users are urged to update their systems as soon as possible.
